@startuml
title Subscription Flow Diagram

|Student|
start
:Open subscription page;
:Review Basic / Silver / Gold plans;
:Choose target upgrade plan;
:Confirm upgrade request;

|Subscription System|
:Verify authenticated user;
:Create upgrade transaction;
if (Running in test/demo mode?) then (Yes)
  :Mark transaction as paid immediately;
  :Upgrade subscription and reset quota instantly;
  |Student|
  :Receive successful upgrade notification;
else (No)
  :Generate SePay reference and QR checkout page;
  |Student|
  :Transfer payment using checkout instructions;
  |System Handler|
  :Receive valid SePay webhook;
  :Match reference code and transfer amount;
  :Update transaction to PAID;
  :Upgrade subscription and reset quota;
  |Student|
  :Use system with updated quota;
endif

stop
@enduml
